Direct Messaging Chat App (Backend)

This project is a WhatsApp-style **1-to-1 direct messaging backend** built with Flask.
It focuses on clean architecture, authentication, and real-time communication,
with the goal of supporting both web and mobile clients.



Features (Current)

- User registration and login
- Secure password hashing
- JWT-based authentication
- Protected routes using JWT
- SQLite database with SQLAlchemy
- Clean, scalable backend structure



Core Design Decisions

- **Direct Messages only** (no public rooms)
- One conversation per pair of users
- Backend-first approach
- Same backend will power:
  - Web app (HTML/CSS/JS)
  - Mobile app (later)



Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- SQLAlchemy
- SQLite
- JWT (PyJWT)
- Werkzeug (password hashing)
- Socket.IO (planned)



