Authentication Endpoints

* Register

POST /auth/register
Body:
{
"username": "john",
"password": "secret123"
}


* Login

POST /auth/login
Body:
{
"username": "john",
"password": "secret123"
}


* Response 

{
"token": "<JWT_TOKEN>",
"user_id": 1
}



The token must be sent in the `Authorization` header for protected routes:




Authorization : Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>





